## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9136e-228">時間會預設為 UTC。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-228">The time will default to UTC.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9136e-229">如果您想要以本機時間指定的時間，則指定<xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A>的屬性`time`物件做為<xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-229">If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9136e-230">下列程式碼連接到伺服器 」 adamHost1.fabrikam.com"連接埠號碼"5000。 」 上裝載的 ADAM 執行個體</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-230">The following code connects to the ADAM instance hosted by the server "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" on port number "5000."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9136e-231">中指定的使用者名稱 (adamAdmin) 和密碼 (SecretPwd123)<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-231">The username (adamAdmin), and password (SecretPwd123) are specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9136e-232">容器下的所有可驗證主體執行搜尋"DC = adamApp1，DC = fabrikam，DC = com"，無法登入這個 ADAM 執行個體過去 45 天內。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-232">A search is performed for all authenticable principals under the container "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com" that have not logged on to this ADAM instance for the last 45 days.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9136e-233">然後會刪除搜尋所傳回的主體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-233">The principals returned by the search are then deleted.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                      ContextType.ApplicationDirectory,   
                                      "adamHost1.fabrikam.com:5000",   
                                      "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                      "adamAdmin", "SecretPwd123");  
  
PrincipalSearchResult<AuthenticablePrincipal> oldPrincipals =   
                     AuthenticablePrincipal.FindByLogonTime(ctx,   
                            (DateTime.Now - new TimeSpan(45, 0, 0, 0)),   
                            MatchType.LessThan);  
  
foreach (Principal p in oldPrincipals)  
{  
    p.Delete();  
}  
  
oldPrincipals.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();  
  
```

