## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9136e-309">下列範例程式碼會連線到 LDAP 網域"fabrikam.com"取代為使用者名稱 （系統管理員），並初始化中的密碼 (SecretPwd123)<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-309">The following example code connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username (administrator) and password (SecretPwd123) initialized in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9136e-310">若要尋找在指定的容器名稱"John Smith"的使用者執行搜尋時<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式:"CN = Users，DC = fabrikam，DC = com。 」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-310">A search is performed to find the user with name "John Smith" under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor: "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9136e-311">如果找到使用者，則會檢查以判斷是否這位使用者的帳戶已被鎖定。如果帳戶已經鎖定時，程式碼範例會解除鎖定帳戶。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9136e-311">If the user is found, a check is performed to determine whether this user's account has been locked out. If the account has been locked out, the code example unlocks the account.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Domain,   
                                         "fabrikam.com",   
                                         "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                         "administrator",   
                                         "SecretPwd123");  
  
UserPrincipal usr = UserPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx, "John Smith");  
if (usr != null)  
{  
    if (usr.IsAccountLockedOut())  
        usr.UnlockAccount();  
  
    usr.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();   
```
